<h1>Account Executive</h1>

<p>Zoovy is looking for assertive, goal-oriented, experienced inside sales reps with the drive to make it to the TOP! Reps will recieve inbound calls from company generated leads and current customers, as well as make outbound telemarketing calls to sell our great e-commerce solution! </p>

<h3>Job Responsibilities: </h3>
<ul>
	<li>B2B telephone sales, including cold calls, inbound AND outbound sales. </li>
	<li>Generating new business and maintaining customer relations. </li>
	<li>Responsible for meeting or exceeding assigned sales goals. </li>
</ul>

<h3>Required Skills: </h3>
<ul>
	<li>Excellent communication skills and phone presence. </li>
	<li>Solid computer related skills and Internet savvy. </li>
	<li>Outbound call presentation and closing skills! </li>
</ul>

<h3>About Zoovy: </h3>

<p>Zoovy provides a full turnkey e-Commerce solution that allows businesses to more effectively manage their online business and increase revenues. Our offering includes a complete Web storefront; secure shopping cart, auction integration, and content management tools developed specifically for ecommerce business owners. </p>

<p>Please review our website for more information www.zoovy.com. Interested, qualified candidates should email your resume to <a href="mailto:jobs@zoovy.com">jobs@zoovy.com</a>.</p>


